{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"5c0ce6ce26de9213ed1377","title":"2026-05-19 Flash 假脱机长图打印开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367059,"created":1780371330026,"custom":{},"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-19_Flash假脱机长图打印开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"ab04cd6505ae9e66c108f25dfc5dae20","links":[{"from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","id":"bk7252n-ai-printer","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":3,"offset":1264},"end":{"line":36,"column":56,"offset":1317},"indent":[]},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-19_Flash假脱机长图打印开发记录"}],"anchors":{"2026-05-19-flash-假脱机长图打印开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"2026-05-19 Flash 假脱机长图打印开发记录","value":"2026-05-19-flash-假脱机长图打印开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"需求背景":{"type":"header","text":"需求背景","value":"需求背景","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"方案选型":{"type":"header","text":"方案选型","value":"方案选型","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2},"最终方案ota-分区假脱机--双模式自适应":{"type":"header","text":"最终方案：OTA 分区假脱机 + 双模式自适应","value":"最终方案ota-分区假脱机--双模式自适应","line":30,"column":0,"depth":2},"核心思路":{"type":"header","text":"核心思路","value":"核心思路","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"互斥策略":{"type":"header","text":"互斥策略","value":"互斥策略","line":46,"column":0,"depth":3},"改动文件清单":{"type":"header","text":"改动文件清单","value":"改动文件清单","line":53,"column":0,"depth":2},"1-thermal_printerh--宏开关--新增接口":{"type":"header","text":"1. thermal_printer.h — 宏开关 + 新增接口","value":"1-thermal_printerh--宏开关--新增接口","line":55,"column":0,"depth":3},"2-thermal_printerc--锁实现--flash-打印函数":{"type":"header","text":"2. thermal_printer.c — 锁实现 + Flash 打印函数","value":"2-thermal_printerc--锁实现--flash-打印函数","line":70,"column":0,"depth":3},"3-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc--双模式接收--flash-打印线程":{"type":"header","text":"3. mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c — 双模式接收 + Flash 打印线程","value":"3-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc--双模式接收--flash-打印线程","line":78,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-ota_upgradec--ota-互斥":{"type":"header","text":"4. OTA_Upgrade.c — OTA 互斥","value":"4-ota_upgradec--ota-互斥","line":116,"column":0,"depth":3},"数据流对比":{"type":"header","text":"数据流对比","value":"数据流对比","line":129,"column":0,"depth":2},"小图28kb路径不变":{"type":"header","text":"小图（≤28KB，路径不变）","value":"小图28kb路径不变","line":131,"column":0,"depth":3},"大图28kbflash-路径":{"type":"header","text":"大图（>28KB，Flash 路径）","value":"大图28kbflash-路径","line":137,"column":0,"depth":3},"启用方式":{"type":"header","text":"启用方式","value":"启用方式","line":155,"column":0,"depth":2},"注意事项":{"type":"header","text":"注意事项","value":"注意事项","line":169,"column":0,"depth":2},"测试要点":{"type":"header","text":"测试要点","value":"测试要点","line":177,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"wn668uyx88v4u3xlc5q5uka","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"2026-05-19-flash-假脱机长图打印开发记录\">2026-05-19 Flash 假脱机长图打印开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-19-flash-假脱机长图打印开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"2026-05-19-flash-假脱机长图打印开发记录-1\">2026-05-19 Flash 假脱机长图打印开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-19-flash-假脱机长图打印开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"需求背景\">需求背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#需求背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>BK7252N 内部 RAM 仅 256KB，扣除 Wi-Fi / MQTT / LVGL / 音频等模块后，可用于打印图片的堆内存不足 30KB。MQTT <code>imagePrint</code> 接收图片使用 28KB 共享缓冲区（<code>MQTT_BINARY_SHARED_BUF_SIZE = 28KB</code>），对应 384 宽热敏位图约 597 行（~7cm 纸长），超过此长度的图片直接拒绝，无法打印。</p>\n<p>硬件条件：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>无 PSRAM</strong>（<code>BEKEN_USING_QSPI_PSRAM_HEAP</code> 未启用，且硬件未焊接 PSRAM）</li>\n<li>Flash 4MB，OTA 分区 1632KB，日常大量闲置</li>\n<li><code>convert_base64_to_print_data</code> 函数未使用（实际走 MQTT 二进制协议）</li>\n<li>流式逐行打印不可行（MQTT 分包可能乱序/丢包/不完整）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"方案选型\">方案选型<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#方案选型\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>方案</th><th>可行性</th><th>原因</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>启用 PSRAM</td><td>?</td><td>硬件无 PSRAM</td></tr><tr><td>流式逐行打印</td><td>?</td><td>MQTT 分包乱序/丢包风险，无法保证完整性</td></tr><tr><td>增大 RAM 缓冲</td><td>?</td><td>内部 RAM 已极度紧张</td></tr><tr><td>压缩传输</td><td>??</td><td>需服务端配合，且解压也耗 RAM</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Flash 假脱机</strong></td><td>?</td><td>复用 OTA 分区，零额外 RAM，与 OTA 互斥</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"最终方案ota-分区假脱机--双模式自适应\">最终方案：OTA 分区假脱机 + 双模式自适应<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#最终方案ota-分区假脱机--双模式自适应\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"核心思路\">核心思路<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#核心思路\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>MQTT 图片接收 → 判断大小\n  ├── ≤28KB → 内存缓冲（快路径，和之前一样）\n  └── >28KB → Flash 假脱机（OTA 分区）\n                ├── 接收时逐包写 Flash\n                └── 收齐后逐行从 Flash 读 48 字节打印\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>内存占用</strong>：始终 48 字节行缓冲，不受图片长度限制</li>\n<li><strong>最大图片</strong>：OTA 分区 1632KB → 384×34000 行 ≈ 4.2 米纸长</li>\n<li><strong>互斥机制</strong>：信号量保护，打印与 OTA 互斥</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"互斥策略\">互斥策略<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#互斥策略\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>  打印进行中 → 来了 OTA → OTA 等待最多 30 秒\n  OTA 进行中 → 来了大图 → 直接拒绝（小图不受影响，不占 OTA 分区）\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"改动文件清单\">改动文件清单<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#改动文件清单\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-thermal_printerh--宏开关--新增接口\">1. <code>thermal_printer.h</code> — 宏开关 + 新增接口<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-thermal_printerh--宏开关--新增接口\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">CFG_PRN_FLASH_SPOOL</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 功能总开关（注释掉即完全禁用）</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// OTA 互斥锁</span>\nbool <span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_spool_lock_try</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">// 非阻塞尝试获取</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_spool_lock_release</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// 释放锁</span>\nbool <span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_spool_is_locked</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">// 查询锁状态</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Flash 逐行打印</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_print_bitmap_from_flash</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">uint32_t</span> flash_offset<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                            <span class=\"token class-name\">uint16_t</span> width<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">uint16_t</span> height<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"2-thermal_printerc--锁实现--flash-打印函数\">2. <code>thermal_printer.c</code> — 锁实现 + Flash 打印函数<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-thermal_printerc--锁实现--flash-打印函数\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>在 <code>thermal_printer_init()</code> 中初始化信号量 <code>s_prn_spool_sem</code></li>\n<li>新增 <code>thermal_printer_print_bitmap_from_flash()</code>：\n<ul>\n<li>逻辑与 <code>thermal_printer_print_bitmap()</code> 完全一致</li>\n<li>区别：行数据通过 <code>bk_flash_read(BK_PARTITION_OTA, offset, line, 48)</code> 逐行读取</li>\n<li>包含完整的白行跳过(white-run)、温度补偿、黑点密度调节等逻辑</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc--双模式接收--flash-打印线程\">3. <code>mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code> — 双模式接收 + Flash 打印线程<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-mqtt_backend_binary_rxc--双模式接收--flash-打印线程\"></a></h3>\n<p><strong>接收会话结构扩展</strong>（<code>mqtt_backend_image_print_rx_ctx_t</code>）：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">ifdef</span> <span class=\"token expression\">CFG_PRN_FLASH_SPOOL</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">rt_bool_t</span> use_flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// 当前会话是否走 Flash</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">uint32_t</span> flash_erase_end<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// Flash 已擦除到的末尾地址</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">endif</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>打印任务结构扩展</strong>（<code>mqtt_backend_print_job_t</code>）：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">ifdef</span> <span class=\"token expression\">CFG_PRN_FLASH_SPOOL</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">rt_bool_t</span> from_flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// 数据在 Flash 而非 RAM</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">uint32_t</span> flash_offset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// Flash 分区内偏移</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">endif</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>关键改动点</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code>mqtt_backend_binary_rx_start_image_print()</code> — 智能路径选择：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>total_size > 28KB</code> 且 <code>CFG_PRN_FLASH_SPOOL</code> 启用 → Flash 模式</li>\n<li>获取 OTA 互斥锁 → 擦除 OTA 分区 → 设置 <code>use_flash = true</code></li>\n<li><code>total_size ≤ 28KB</code> → 走原 RAM 路径</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>mqtt_backend_binary_rx_feed_image_print()</code> — Flash 写路径：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flash 模式：<code>bk_flash_write(BK_PARTITION_OTA, recv_size, data, len)</code></li>\n<li>RAM 模式：<code>memcpy()</code> 到共享缓冲区</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>mqtt_backend_spawn_print_flash()</code> — Flash 打印线程创建：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置 <code>from_flash = true, flash_offset = 0</code></li>\n<li>打印线程结束后释放 OTA 锁</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>mqtt_backend_print_worker()</code> — 双模式打印：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flash 模式：调用 <code>thermal_printer_print_bitmap_from_flash()</code></li>\n<li>RAM 模式：调用 <code>thermal_printer_print_bitmap()</code></li>\n<li>退出时 Flash 模式自动释放 OTA 锁</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"4-ota_upgradec--ota-互斥\">4. <code>OTA_Upgrade.c</code> — OTA 互斥<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-ota_upgradec--ota-互斥\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ota_upgrade_thread_entry() 开头</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_spool_is_locked</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;&#x26;</span> wait_cnt <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">rt_thread_mdelay</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 等待打印完成，最多 30 秒</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_spool_lock_try</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 获取锁，阻止后续打印</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// __exit 标签处</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">thermal_printer_spool_lock_release</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 释放锁</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"数据流对比\">数据流对比<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#数据流对比\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"小图28kb路径不变\">小图（≤28KB，路径不变）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#小图28kb路径不变\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>MQTT → 28KB 共享 RAM 缓冲 → 打印线程 → thermal_printer_print_bitmap()\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"大图28kbflash-路径\">大图（>28KB，Flash 路径）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#大图28kbflash-路径\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>MQTT ──逐包──→ bk_flash_write(BK_PARTITION_OTA, ...)\n                       │\n              (全部收齐，CRC 隐含在协议层)\n                       │\n                       ▼\n              打印线程启动（持 OTA 锁）\n                       │\n            for (y = 0; y &#x3C; height; y++)\n              bk_flash_read(OTA, y*48, line, 48);\n              print_line(line, heat_us);\n                       │\n                       ▼\n              释放 OTA 锁\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"启用方式\">启用方式<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#启用方式\"></a></h2>\n<p>在 <code>applications/Printer/thermal_printer.h</code> 中：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 改前</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// #define CFG_PRN_FLASH_SPOOL</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 改后</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">CFG_PRN_FLASH_SPOOL</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>重新编译：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n -j4</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项\">注意事项<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#注意事项\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>仅对 <code>imagePrint</code> 命令生效</strong>，<code>audioChunk</code>（语音生成图）仍走纯 RAM 路径</li>\n<li>Flash 擦除为扇区对齐（4KB），会擦除比实际需求略多的空间</li>\n<li>OTA 分区原始数据在打印后会被覆盖，下次 OTA 前服务端必须重新下发完整固件</li>\n<li>打印期间来了 OTA 指令 → OTA 等待。若打印卡死（硬件故障）最长等待 30 秒后强行走 OTA</li>\n<li>若 Flash 为 2MB（<code>FLASH_SELECTION_TYPE_2M</code>），OTA 分区仅 560KB，仍可打印约 12000 行</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"测试要点\">测试要点<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#测试要点\"></a></h2>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 小图（&#x3C;28KB）打印正常，不受影响</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 大图（>28KB）通过 Flash 路径正常打印</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 打印期间触发 OTA → OTA 等待/超时</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> OTA 期间发送大图打印 → 拒绝</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 宏关闭后所有功能回退到原有行为</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Flash 写入后 CRC 校验通过（隐含在 MQTT 分包协议中）</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/bk7252n-ai-printer\">BK7252N AI 打印机</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"个人开发笔记（Dendron 多项目知识库）","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"185a3f748171123c20ed21d8566347c8","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":51},"end":{"line":8,"column":9,"offset":57},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"D